# Emacs
###############################################################################
#
HOTKEYS_TEXT_EMACS="C-z   - switch keyboard language
M-g              - go to line
C-x 2            - horizontal split
C-x 3            - vertical split
M-x untabify     - remove tabs from file
M-x recover-file - recover unsaved file

M-x template-latex-report       - create LaTeX report in current catalog
M-x template-latex-presentation - create LaTeX presentation in current
                                  catalog
C-c C-c                         - build or view LaTeX source
C-c C-e                         - insert environment
C-c C-s                         - insert heading
F12                             - enable syntax checking (by aspell)
C-c =                           - show ToC
C-s M-r                         - regexp search
C-r M-r                         - reverse regexp search
M-% (after search starts)       - query replace (\(\) - group)

F8          - jump to imports
M-.         - jump to definition
C-c C-z     - navigate between errors
M-n         - go to next error or warning
M-p         - go to previous error or warning
M-?         - show error or warning information

C-c C-c     - run Haskell compiler for current file
TAB         - show next compile error
RET         - goto compile error
g           - recompile
q           - quit compile window

C-c C-l     - load current file into REPL
F1          - open REPL buffer
M-n         - next line in history
M-p         - previous line in history
C-c C-k     - clear REPL"

